title: Crash Bandicoot: Warped
summary: Crash Bandicoot: Warped, known in Europe as Crash Bandicoot 3: Warped,[2][3] is a 1998 platform game developed by Naughty Dog and published by Sony Computer Entertainment for the PlayStation. It is the third game in the Crash Bandicoot video game series following Crash Bandicoot 2: Cortex Strikes Back.
